<main class="carousel-body" role="main">

      <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="10000">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="first-slide" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAHd3dwAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="First slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
                <h1>Make data collection exhaustive and effortless.</h1>
                <p>We transform rough inputs and structure them to fit a customized framework.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="phase1" role="button">Discover more &raquo;</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="second-slide" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAHd3dwAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="Second slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h1>Overcome supply chain complexity and opacity.</h1>
                <p>We collect the requested data from suppliers and we manage the level of granularity to be shared.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="phase2" role="button">Discover more &raquo;</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="third-slide" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAHd3dwAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption text-right">
                <h1>Turn sustainable ambitions into measurable actions.</h1>
                <p>We provide tools to assess and modelize products'CSR performance based on current and future achievements.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="phase3" role="button">Discover more &raquo;</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="third-slide" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAHd3dwAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption text-right">
                <h1>Give consumers next level of transparency.</h1>
                <p>We transform collected data to directly fill in scoring, certifications, and other CSR assessment forms.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="phase4" role="button">Discover more &raquo;</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>


      <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
      ================================================== -->
      <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

      <div class="container marketing">

        <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-3">
            <%= image_tag "step1.png", class:"rounded-circle", width:"140", height:"140" %>    
            <h2><span>1- Collect<span><br/>
            <span>brand data<span></h2>
            <p> An accurate supply chain traceability starts with a robust and comprehensive data baseline.</p><br/>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="phase1" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-3">
            <%= image_tag "step2.png", class:"rounded-circle", width:"140", height:"140" %>  
            <h2><span>2- Trace back<span><br/>
            <span>operations<span></h2>
            <p>Traceability requires the connection of multiple partners and the ability to make them collaborate by sharing their data.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="phase2" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-3">
            <%= image_tag "step3.png", class:"rounded-circle", width:"140", height:"140" %>  
            <h2><span>3- Analyze<span><br/>
            <span>CSR performance<span></h2>
            <p>Spread out data finally gathered still needs to be transformed into relevant insights to be highly valuable.</p><br/>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="phase3" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-3">
            <%= image_tag "step4.png", class:"rounded-circle", width:"140", height:"140" %>  
            <h2><span>4- Leverage<span><br/>
            <span>Traceability data<span></h2>
            <p>Transfer this data to access a wide network of fashion CSR solutions promoting transparency and circularity.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="phase4" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        </div><!-- /.row -->


        <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7" style="text-align:left">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">A set of tools to <span class="text-muted">make data collection exhaustive and effortless.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Onboard all the relevant stakeholders who can upload, fill or push their information on the platform. We transform rough inputs into structured ones to initiate product traceability.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <%= image_tag "step1bis.png", class:"featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto", width:"150", height:"150"%>  
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2" style="text-align:right">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">A solution to <span class="text-muted">overcome supply chain complexity and opacity.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Acquire a wide understanding of your products’supply chain by letting us bridge data sources from partners involved. As a third party, we preserve the confidentiality suppliers require : we collect the requested data and we manage the level of granularity to be shared.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
            <%= image_tag "step2bis.png", class:"featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto", width:"150", height:"150"%>  
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7" style="text-align:left">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Advanced analytic supports to <span class="text-muted">turn sustainable ambitions into measurable actions.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Steer or adjust your CSR action plan with a clear overview of your products’ CSR performance. We provide you the tools to assess and modelize them based on your current and future achievements.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <%= image_tag "step3bis.png", class:"featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto", width:"150", height:"150"%>  
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2" style="text-align:right">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Data sharing enablers to <span class="text-muted">give consumers next level of transparency.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">Leverage your data by transferring them seamlessly to multiple fashion CSR solutions. We transform your set of collected data to directly fill in scoring, certifications, and other CSR assessment forms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
            <%= image_tag "step4bis.png", class:"featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto", width:"150", height:"150"%>  
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        

        <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

      </div><!-- /.container -->
</main>